{"tid":1781664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周梓樂父母發聲明　感謝各方鼓勵祝福　「祝願香港平安」","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T09:42:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7458c51bdbd72bb4ee0fb5ffc188af2a64649a9f","tid":1781664,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"科大學生周梓樂 11 月 8 日在尚德停車場身亡，今日出殯；周梓樂的爸爸、媽媽向傳媒發放聲明，指周梓樂的喪禮告一段落，感謝各方人士包括親朋好友「前來與梓樂作最後的道別」，他們感謝各方的鼓勵和祝福，令他們有力量渡過艱難時刻，「最後，我們再一次向大家誠懇致謝，祝願香港平安」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又特別感謝在過去一段時間提供協助的單位，包括周梓樂留醫的伊利沙伯醫院，他就讀的香港科技大學、宣基中學，儀式舉行的寶福紀念館等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chow-22_FTRmC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchow-22_FTRmC_1200x0.png&h=41ecbe51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F-%E7%A5%9D%E9%A1%98%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%25A6%258F-%25E7%25A5%259D%25E9%25A1%2598%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%2589%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=12132d7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%25A6%258F-%25E7%25A5%259D%25E9%25A1%2598%25E9%25A6%2599%